Name: Dogs Cyberpuzzle
About the game: A jigsaw puzzle like you've never seen before . Drag & drop and rotate the pieces to complete the puzzles within the time limit . Time gets shorter and shorter as the levels go by. 2 videos per level so you can solve the puzzles placing the pieces strategically according to the areas of each video. Enjoy the awesome synthwave tracks . 51 Achievements. Are you fast enough to unlock all of them? Finish the game to unlock Kitty's message . It contains extremely important information about the future . .. ..
